  Advanced Face Swapping

In this video, I'll show you how to perform advanced face swapping techniques using FaceFusion and Pinokio. Unlike most of the AI techniques shown throughout this course, this technique uses your local machine and open source code to create the video.

As a result, you may run into instances of the tool crashing or becoming inoperable on your machine. If this happens to you, no sweat. You can still use online tools like Akool for Face Swapping. The results are close, but the following video is just a little more advanced.
